099">have the following=20
properties:<br>1) ONE pair of opposite sides are parallel.=20
(BC and AD)<br>
=20

2) The sum of the angles attached to the <i>same</i> leg =3D 180=C2=B0<br>=
=20
=20
&nbsp; &nbsp; =E2=88=A0 'A' plus =E2=88=A0 'B' =3D 180=C2=B0  <br>
&nbsp; &nbsp; =E2=88=A0 'C' plus =E2=88=A0 'D' =3D 180=C2=B0 <br>
=20
</font></font></font></p></font></font></font></center><p><font size=3D"5">=
